Wacky Tuesday Bible Study - 12:00 Noon Wednesday Night "Upbeat" Bible Study - 6:00 P.M. Greetings from the Congregation and Ministries of Salem United Methodist Church. We welcome you to share the joy of our Lord through worship and teaching. Here, you will be part of a loving family dedicated to reaching out to all in need of care and healing. We are an innovative and progressive community based church that has many active ministries that will appeal to all age groups. Whether it is traditional worship or simply fellowship we have something to meet your needs. Please visit our website at http://www.salemumcorange.org for more information. Join us this Sunday in worship and take the first step towards spiritual rejuvenation.
